snippet.textDisplay:
Aaaaannnnnnnddddddd now we have the most intense song of the season!

From Sufi music with Abida Jee and Naseebo to badass queen stuff by Eva B, soothing melodies by Asfar Hussain and Arooj Aftab and funky beats with Ali Sethi and Shae Gill, now is the time for the intense song!

I just love the sequence CS14 has chosen for releasing its songs. 

Talha & Faris gave us the strongest, best and bravest rap and Karakoram gave us excellent vocals. I'm in love!!!!!!!!!!

Great, great, great job once again! ❤️❤️❤️❤️
